{"tid":2311362,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《蘋果日報》告讀者書：我們不會認命","createTime":"2020-12-04T04:15:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T13:16:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c6f97593713a5d34ad25fc6321a1ef1f1f2eee75","tid":2311362,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T04:15:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201204/4YFNOZYNGJFUHGZHSEVYSZUAMM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201204%2F4YFNOZYNGJFUHGZHSEVYSZUAMM%2F&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGPrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=72ed44a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201204%2F4YFNOZYNGJFUHGZHSEVYSZUAMM%2F&h=c13f2487\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201204/4YFNOZYNGJFUHGZHSEVYSZUAMM/</a><br />\n<br />\n《蘋果日報》告讀者書：我們不會認命<br />\n<br />\n各位讀者：<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：涉違租契 國安官禁保釋  黎智英成政治囚徒<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果日報》創立25年，今日是令人特別難過一天，我們的創辦人黎智英先生被政權打壓，將被還柙至明年4月。<br />\n<br />\n自黎先生和一眾管理層被捕三個多月來，《蘋果》一直未有鬆懈，繼續做好新聞，監察政府，擁抱自由民主；在未來黎先生被困獄中無法和我們一起打拼的日子，《蘋果》上下會一直緊守崗位，懇請各位繼續支持。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：黎周持力高股份 黃助改地址<br />\n一如黎先生在《蘋果》20周年特刊序言提到：「當歷史巨輪輾壓到你頭頂上來了，每個毛孔都充滿恐懼時，你仍不認命才重要。」<br />\n<br />\n有香港人就有《蘋果》。我們不會認命，謹與全體香港人共勉。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果日報》仝人<br />\n<br />\n2020年12月3日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/oeZKaJfSFKQeejaAChy2QtVw2nI=/4872x3248/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KMUXHLSBEVB5FNN3CLKBUGECIY.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FoeZKaJfSFKQeejaAChy2QtVw2nI%3D%2F4872x3248%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKMUXHLSBEVB5FNN3CLKBUGECIY.JPG&h=b72d4b46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蘋果日報大樓"},{"pid":"b20340e7a4c83715d0467a13b51be23a379ec629","tid":2311362,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T06:27:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cc1e27428af9548bcd299138e10521adbd83975","tid":2311362,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T07:53:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88b26ec27e401240cafce39c3d5748038f53d8ec","tid":2311362,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T10:33:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14a81936209145ac4ef433d95c01c5011c2cfcae","tid":2311362,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T13:16:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}